OL,7,F"It's extremely stressful. It's this
OL,8,Fcloud that's been over me for a very
OL,9,Flong time and I just want to get it
OL,10,Ffixed."
OL,12,FLucy is one of thousands of residents
OL,13,Fwho say the new government must step
OL,14,Fin to help those living in homes
OL,15,Fdeemed unsafe following the Grenfell
OL,16,Ftower fire in 2017 when 72 people lost
OL,17,Ftheir lives.
