OL,3,C'Trapped in a home I can't sell':
OL,4,CResident's plea as cladding causes
OL,5,Cfire hazard
OL,7,F"The government encouraged me to get
OL,8,Fon the property ladder and actually
OL,9,Fhelped me to do so," she said. "Now
OL,10,Fit's turning its back on me and many
OL,11,Fin the same position."
OL,13,FLucy's block of 20 flats is under 11
OL,14,Fmetres tall, below the height deemed a
OL,15,Frisk to life. But the recent
OL,16,Fdevastating fire in a block in
OL,17,FDagenham, East London shows, says
OL,18,FLucy, that all blocks with safety
OL,19,Fissues need the same protection.
