OL,7,FThe developers of the Bristol block,
OL,8,FClayewater Homes, said it appreciated
OL,9,Fthe stress for leaseholders but it had
OL,10,Fno legal or contractual responsibility
OL,11,Ffor any further works given it met
OL,12,Fbuilding regulations when the property
OL,13,Fwas completed in 2016.
OL,15,F"We built and then sold Clayewater
OL,16,FCourt in 2016/17, meeting the
OL,17,Frequirements of all relevant building
OL,18,Fregulations in force at the time," it
OL,19,Fadded.
